EmailTemplate.subject: Recap of the QuickBooks Payments Program
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Account #{!Contact.CAN__c}
Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
It was great speaking with you today. You are now ready to start accepting payments and sending E-Invoices in your QuickBooks Enterprise Solutions. Here is that list of articles that you and I spoke about to help you get the most out of this new addition to your software.
Access Merchant Service Center from in QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW16081
Add/change users in Merchant Service Center: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW18133
Create E-invoices: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW25240
Create Recurring Payments in QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW16018
Processing Card Payments in QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW16764
Perform Void, Refund, Reverse or credit in QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/HOW15994
Accept Check Payment by phone: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/pages/inproducthelp/Core/QB2K12/ContentPackage/Services/Merchant/svc_qbms_key_enter_checks.html
Download Fees and Adjustments into QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/pages/inproducthelp/Core/QB2K12/ContentPackage/Core/Deposit/df_fees_and_adjustment_helpid.html
Reconcile Merchant Services in QuickBooks: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/pages/inproducthelp/Core/QB2K12/ContentPackage/Core/Deposit/f1_dep_total_diffs.html
We at Intuit value your business and are continuously working to improve the experience we provide to our most valued customers and are excited to offer you this new benefit.
{!User.FirstName} {!User.LastName}| Enterprise Account Manager Work Phone: {!User.Phone} ext {!User.Extension} | {!User.Email}
Intuit | simplify the business of life
